*logmon-0.4.4-r1 (03 Apr 2013)

  03 Apr 2013; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> +logmon-0.4.4-r1.ebuild,
  logmon-0.4.4.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Extensively tested. Cleaned up ebuild; EAPI 5, replaced src_unpack by
  src_prepare and removed unnecessary die. Added missing glibc dependency, bump
  because binary changed as well as to avoid breaking stable.

  13 Mar 2013; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Took maintainership.

  22 Nov 2011; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop maintainer due retirement, bug #82110

  18 Dec 2008; Peter Alfredsen <loki_val@gentoo.org>
  +files/logmon-0.4.4-gcc43.patch,
  +files/logmon-0.4.4-maintainer-mode.patch, logmon-0.4.4.ebuild:
  Fix bug 226677. Thanks to Naohiro Aota for gcc-4.3 fix. Also fixed QA:
  Maintainer Mode detected.

  20 Aug 2006; <malc@gentoo.org> logmon-0.4.4.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64

  07 May 2006; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> logmon-0.4.4.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

  25 Feb 2006; Marcelo Goes <vanquirius@gentoo.org> logmon-0.4.4.ebuild:
  Mark 0.4.4 x86 stable.

  23 Jan 2006; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> logmon-0.4.4.ebuild:
